@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml

top to bottom direction
title FIG-10-02. Online Store Bounded Context Map

skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 70

rectangle "Catalogue Context\n<<Upstream>>\nProduct, price,\navailability" as Catalogue #EAF6E8
rectangle "Ordering Context\n<<Downstream of Catalogue>>\nBasket, order,\norder line" as Ordering #FFFFFF
rectangle "Payment Context\n<<Supplier to Ordering>>\nPayment attempt,\nauthorisation" as Payment #F7F9FB
rectangle "Fulfilment Context\n<<Supplier to Ordering>>\nShipment,\ndelivery status" as Fulfilment #F7F9FB
rectangle "Support Context\n<<Downstream>>\nReturn, refund request,\ncase" as Support #FFFFFF

rectangle "Payment Provider System\n<<External system>>" as PayProvider #F2F5F7
rectangle "Delivery Partner System\n<<External system>>" as DeliveryPartner #F2F5F7
rectangle "Payment Provider ACL\n<<Anti-Corruption Layer>>" as PayACL #FFF4D6
rectangle "Delivery Partner ACL\n<<Anti-Corruption Layer>>" as DeliveryACL #FFF4D6

Catalogue -down-> Ordering : R1

Ordering -left-> Payment : R2
Payment -right-> Ordering : R3

Ordering -right-> Fulfilment : R4
Fulfilment -left-> Ordering : R5

Support -up-> Ordering : R6
Support -up-> Fulfilment : R7
Support ..> Support : R8

Payment -down-> PayACL : ACL
PayACL -down-> PayProvider : translate
Fulfilment -down-> DeliveryACL : ACL
DeliveryACL -down-> DeliveryPartner : translate

legend bottom
Context map, not deployment view.
R1 Catalogue upstream -> Ordering downstream: Open Host Service + Published Language.
R2 Ordering -> Payment: Customer/Supplier payment authorisation.
R3 Payment -> Ordering: Published Language, PaymentAuthorised.
R4 Ordering -> Fulfilment: Customer/Supplier fulfilment request.
R5 Fulfilment -> Ordering: Published Language, shipment status.
R6/R7 Support is Conformist to selected order and shipment status terms.
R8 Support uses Separate Ways for internal case handling.
ACL means Anti-Corruption Layer and marks translation boundaries to external systems.
endlegend
@enduml
